data.description: This like new home in the city of North Pole may bring more joy then just living close to Santa Claus!  Five star plus when built, this baby sips the heating oil with its efficient design including 2x8 construction, triple pane windows, and a Buderous Boiler.  The living area is open and features a vaulted ceiling.  It flows directly into the dining room and the you can't miss kitchen.  So much space on the counter and in the cabinetry.  There's a great walk in pantry and more downstairs.  The upstairs consists of all three bedrooms, including the master suite where you'll find your walk in shower, double vanity, and walk in closet.  There is a full bathroom for the other two bedrooms and your laundry room upstairs, no hauling laundry anywhere! Outside there has been a lawn and large driveway already done, and you can fit a ton of your stuff in the three car garage.  Check this one out!
